data.description: Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac of well maintained homes and yards in Pine Lakes, this home is within walking distance to the Pines Golf Course! Four bedrooms, den/office, three baths with a two car side entry garage. From the moment you drive onto the stamped concrete driveway, you feel the pride of ownership that was given to this home. Upon entering the screen enclosed with awning front entryway, you will marvel at the great room with formal dining room layout, the extras and details that went into this home. From the crown molding, trey ceiling, chair rails, niches, plant shelves, built-in glassed etched door pantry, tile and wood floors, light fixtures, ceiling fans, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and high end bathroom vanities, the list goes on! Completing this home is an enclosed 39x7 tiled lanai with a door into one of the guest bathrooms in anticipation for a future pool bath and door leading to the rear yard. Home comes with a 22KW Generac whole house generator and two 100 gallon propane tanks. This is a must see home Priced to Sell!
